    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use the <a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-javadoc-plugin/apidocs/org/apache/maven/plugin/javadoc/AbstractJavadocMojo.html#skip\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>maven.javadoc.skip</code></a> property to skip execution of the plugin, going by the Mojo's javadoc. You can specify the value as a Maven property:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;maven.javadoc.skip&gt;true&lt;/maven.javadoc.skip&gt;\n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or as a command-line argument: <code>-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true</code>, to skip generation of the Javadocs.</p>\n"
  }, {
