      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "This didn&#39;t work for me, but learned that when you use the maven release plugin you need to pass this parameter differently.  This worked: <code>mvn release:perform -Darguments=&quot;-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true&quot;</code>."
