    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>It seems, that the simple way</p>\n\n<pre><code>-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>does not work with the release-plugin. in this case you have to pass the parameter as an \"argument\"</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn release:perform -Darguments=\"-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true\"\n</code></pre>\n"
