    "body" : "<p>For newbie Powershell users it is important to know that '.' is  a syntactic element of Powershell, so the switch has to be enclosed in double quotes:</p>\n\n<p>mvn clean install \"-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true\"</p>\n"
