    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>One important thing is:\nif you set <code>&lt;skip&gt;false&lt;skip&gt;</code> in configuration of maven-javadoc-plugin in pom.xml, the <code>-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true</code> will not work, at least for maven-daemon(aka mvndaemon or mvnd).</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3719415,
      "reputation" : 157,
      "user_id" : 3094794,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f6888483b5d4343e23381f5efdebdeb3?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "David",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3094794/david"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 7,
    "last_activity_date" : 1665729641,
    "creation_date" : 1665729641,
    "answer_id" : 74065269,
    "question_id" : 7412016,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Dans le pom.xml</p>\n<p>1st option : using properties</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;properties&gt;\n    &lt;maven.javadoc.skip&gt;true&lt;/maven.javadoc.skip&gt; \n&lt;/properties&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>2nd option : using the build &gt; pluginManagement &gt; plugins &gt; plugin &gt; configuration</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;build&gt;\n    &lt;pluginManagement&gt;\n        &lt;plugins&gt;\n            &lt;plugin&gt;\n                &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n                &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-release-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n                &lt;version&gt;2.5.3&lt;/version&gt;\n                &lt;configuration&gt;\n                    &lt;goals&gt;deploy&lt;/goals&gt;\n                    &lt;arguments&gt;-Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true&lt;/arguments&gt;\n                &lt;/configuration&gt;\n            &lt;/plugin&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>3rd option : When invoking mvn (this one did not work for me)</p>\n<pre><code> mvn clean install -Dmaven.javadoc.skip=true\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
